These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit, goat, goldfish
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, woodworking, card-games, hiking
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
3. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
5. the person who's hobby is baking is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the owner of the goat is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Pet      | goldfish  | frog | rabbit  | goat |
| Hobby   | card-games | hiking      | baking | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
House: ranch-style, cottage, colonial, futuristic
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, gardening, chess, rock-climbing
1. the cottage house is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
2. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the futuristic house##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| House   | futuristic | colonial | cottage   | ranch-style |
| Hobby           | chess      | hiking    | gardening | rock-climbing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
House: cape-cod, palace, victorian, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, june, november, september
1. the palace house is the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the palace house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
5. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
6. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| House        | palace | cape-cod | victorian     | gothic-revival |
| Birthday   | june  | september   | november | december    |

