.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, surfing, skateboarding, baseball
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, fish, bird, rabbit
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the fish##2
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Sport         | skateboarding | biathlon | surfing | baseball |
| Pet   | rabbit   | bird     | fish    | hedgehog       |

