.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, pakistani, chinese, polish
City: venice, liverpool, edinburgh, new-york
1. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
2. the polish is on the left or right of the chinese##3
3. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
6. the polish is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Nationality          | chinese | polish   | colombian   | pakistani    |
| City   | liverpool  | new-york | venice | edinburgh |

