The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, puzzles, card-games, skydiving
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Flower           | tulip | sunflower | balloon-flower | azalea |
| Hobby   | card-games        | skydiving     | chess       | puzzles   |

