.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, dancer, photographer, police-officer
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, blue, orange, turquise
1. the person who likes blue is the police-officer##1
2. the dressmaker is between the dancer and the person who likes orange##2
3. the person who likes emerald is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
5. the dressmaker is in an even position##4
6. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Job   | dancer | dressmaker  | photographer  | police-officer   |
| Color           | turquise  | emerald | orange | blue |

