.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, mirinda, hot-chocolate
4 different games are played: poker, backgammon, go, chess
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up     | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | lemonade   |
| Game    | chess | backgammon  | go | poker |

