.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, asparagus, cabbage, zucchini
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, game, prince, bongani
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
2. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the game-smoker##5
4. the person eating spinach is the prince-smoker##1
5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
6. the game-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Food   | spinach | cabbage        | zucchini        | asparagus |
| Cigar         | prince  | bongani | havana | game |

