3. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
4. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
6. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's sport is climbing##1

