.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, train, car
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, analyst, engineer, project-manager
1. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
2. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
3. the analyst is on the left of the project-manager##1
4. the project-manager is the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
6. the analyst is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport   | car  | bike | quad-bike | train |
| Job   | engineer | coach | analyst   | project-manager  |

