4. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the colonial house##5
5. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
6. the colonial house is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
