.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, mystery, superhero, disaster
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, july, october
1. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
5. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
6. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching western movies and the person who's birthday is in march##2
7. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | western   | superhero  | mystery      | disaster       |
| Birthday   | july | october | march | january |

