The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing, baseball, lacrosse
1. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
2. the fan of rock is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | dubstep | folk | rock |
| Sport     | sailing | biathlon    | baseball    | lacrosse |

