2. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
3. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the fan of soul##5
4. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
5. the tower house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
6. the fan of soul is between the fan of classical and the cape-cod house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Music-Genre      | indie     | classical | soul     | pop |
| House   | art-deco | craftsman  | tower | cape-cod        |

