There 4 different types of food: banana, grapefruit, peach, cauliflower
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person eating grapefruit and the person drinking almond-milk##2
2. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate   | 7up   | fanta       | almond-milk   |
| Food   | peach | grapefruit | banana | cauliflower |

