.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, milk, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, daisy, aconite
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5
6. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who growspoppy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage        | 7up     | soy-milk | lemonade | milk |
| Flower   | daisy | aconite | amaryllis      | poppy        |

 